HIS APARTMENT --

44:31.660 --> 44:34.788
HE HAD ALL THIS KID STUFF --
GAMES,

44:34.840 --> 44:38.139
YOU KNOW,
STUFF HENRY PLAYS WITH.

44:38.170 --> 44:40.400
IT WAS HARD.

44:42.180 --> 44:44.398
IT WAS HARD, ELIZABETH.

44:47.250 --> 44:48.672
HI.

44:50.350 --> 44:53.217
[Voice breaking ]
NO, I'M NOT.

44:53.250 --> 44:56.310
I'VE BEEN HAVING
A REALLY HARD TIME,

44:56.360 --> 44:59.523
AND I'M HURTING A LOT.

44:59.560 --> 45:01.858
[ Crying ]
I DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.

45:01.900 --> 45:05.825
I ALMOST FEEL LIKE...

45:05.870 --> 45:08.839
WHEN I DO THIS STUFF...

45:08.870 --> 45:10.861
IF I DON'T --

45:17.410 --> 45:20.345
I JUST FEEL LIKE...

45:20.380 --> 45:23.679
FROM NOW ON,
I NEED TO BE ABLE...

45:23.720 --> 45:26.917
TO KNOW...
WHAT I'M DOING BETTER

45:26.950 --> 45:28.952
5-50 I...

45:34.960 --> 45:36.621
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

45:38.460 --> 45:40.098
[ SIGHS ]

45:40.130 --> 45:41.529
[ SNIFFLES ]

45:41.570 --> 45:44.232
I'VE TRIED PRAYING,
AND IT DOESN'T HELP.

45:44.270 --> 45:45.532
CAN YOU PLEASE...

45:45.570 --> 45:47.709
[ BREATHES SHAKILY ]

45:47.740 --> 45:49.879
...PLEASE HELP ME?

45:49.910 --> 45:54.074
[ SIGHS ]
I GUESS I JUST FEEL LIKE...

45:54.110 --> 45:56.249
[ SIGHS ]

46:01.250 --> 46:02.786
Wallace: THE PRESIDENT LAUNCHED
A NEW OFFENSIVE

46:02.820 --> 46:04.617
AGAINST THE NUCLEAR FREEZE
MOVEMENT.

46:04.660 --> 46:05.888
ADDRESSING A CONVENTION
OF EVANGELICALS,

46:05.930 --> 46:07.420
ONWARD CHRISTIAN SOLDIERS...

46:07.460 --> 46:10.896
HOLD ON.
W-WE SHOULD LISTEN TO THIS.

46:10.930 --> 46:13.069
[ VOLUME INCREASES ]
...AGAINST THE ARMS FREEZE
FROM THEIR PULPITS.

46:13.100 --> 46:14.795
President Reagan:
SIMPLEMINDED APPEASEMENT

46:14.840 --> 46:17.934
OR WISHFUL THINKING
ABOUT OUR ADVERSARIES IS FOLLY.

46:17.970 --> 46:19.767
IT MEANS
THE BETRAYAL OF OUR PAST,

46:19.810 --> 46:21.437
THE SQUANDERING
OF OUR FREEDOM.

46:21.470 --> 46:22.903
I CAN'T TAKE IT.

46:22.940 --> 46:25.101
THEY'RE JUST -- THEY'RE LIARS.

46:25.150 --> 46:27.801
THEY'RE LIARS, AND THEY'RE
TRYING TO TURN ME INTO ONE.

46:27.850 --> 46:30.068
Wallace: MR. REAGAN CAST
THE US. CONFRONTATION

46:30.120 --> 46:32.247
WITH THE SOVIET UNION
IN MORAL TERMS,

46:32.290 --> 46:34.918
USING SOME OF THE SHARPEST
LANGUAGE OF HIS PRESIDENCY

46:34.960 --> 46:36.757
TO CONDEMN SOVIET LEADERS.

46:36.790 --> 46:38.985
IN YOUR DISCUSSIONS OF
THE NUCLEAR FREEZE PROPOSALS,

46:39.030 --> 46:41.453
I URGE YOU TO BEWARE
THE TEMPTATION OF PRIDE,

46:41.490 --> 46:45.267
THE TEMPTATION OF
BLITHELY DECLARING
YOURSELVES ABOVE IT ALL...

46:45.300 --> 46:47.768
OHH!
YES!
...AND LABEL BOTH SIDES
EQUALLY AT FAULT.

46:47.800 --> 46:50.598
THEY'RE [SNIFFLES] THEY'RE NOT
WHO THEY SAY THEY ARE.

46:50.640 --> 46:52.767
THEY'RE NOT...AMERICANS.

46:52.810 --> 46:54.459
...TO IGNORE
THE FACTS OF HISTORY

46:54.510 --> 46:56.501
AND THE AGGRESSIVE IMPULSES
OF AN EVIL EMPIRE,

46:56.540 --> 46:59.976
TO SIMPLY CALL THE ARMS RACE
A GIANT MISUNDERSTANDING,

47:00.010 --> 47:02.114
AND THEREBY REMOVE YOURSELF
FROM THE STRUGGLE

47:02.150 --> 47:04.948
BETWEEN RIGHT AND WRONG
AND GOOD AND EVIL.

47:04.990 --> 47:07.140
I'M -- I'M NOT
SUPPOSED TO SAY IT.

47:07.190 --> 47:11.957
Y-YOU CAN'T TELL ANYONE.

47:11.990 --> 47:14.288
THEY'RE...

47:14.330 --> 47:17.356
TH EY'RE...RUSSIANS.

47:17.400 --> 47:20.460
...WHILE THEY PREACH
THE SUPREMACY OF THE STATE,

47:20.500 --> 47:22.832
DECLARE ITS OMNIPOTENCE
OVER INDIVIDUAL MAN

47:22.870 --> 47:24.838
AND PREDICT
ITS EVENTUAL DOMINATION

47:24.870 --> 47:26.701
OF ALL PEOPLES ON THE EARTH.

47:26.740 --> 47:29.971
THEY ARE THE FOCUS OF EVIL
IN THE MODERN WORLD.

47:30.010 --> 47:31.875
[ APPLAUSE ]
